frames.caption: A couple lies comfortably on a bed of fluffy pink clouds, creating a dreamy and surreal scene. The woman is dressed in a flowing pink gown, while the man, in a suit, holds up a glass of rosé wine. Their relaxed postures and serene expressions suggest a moment of bliss and celebration.
frames.description: The scene depicts a couple enjoying a whimsical moment on a cloud-like setting, evoking a sense of romance and fantasy. The use of soft pink tones and the ethereal quality of the clouds contribute to the dreamlike atmosphere.

frames.caption: A couple is nestled within a heart-shaped cloud formation, surrounded by soft pink clouds. They are gazing at each other lovingly, with the man holding a champagne glass aloft in a celebratory gesture.
frames.description: The scene depicts a romantic and dreamy setting in the sky, where a couple is enveloped in a heart-shaped cloud. The atmosphere is serene and intimate, with a sense of celebration and love.
